    <p>{`In the upper right corner, set the time interval so that you are viewing the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Last hour`}</strong>{` of data.`}</p>
    <p>{`Select the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Quote of the Day`}</strong>{` application
`}<img parentName="p" {...{
