    <p>{`On this page you can see the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Golden Signals`}</strong>{`.  This includes the transaction volumes, the number of erroneous calls, latency, as well as the top services that make up the application.`}</p>
    <p>{`Youll notice that there is a period of time where you can see an increase in the number of `}<strong parentName="p">{`Erroneous Calls`}</strong>{`.  At the same time interval, there is an increase in `}<strong parentName="p">{`Latency`}</strong>{`.  Later, well investigate these conditions in a diagnostic scenario.`}</p>
    <p>{`Youll notice a number of tabs across the top of the screen.  Explore these tabs.  In particular, lets take a look at the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Depedencies`}</strong>{` tab.
`}<img parentName="p" {...{
        "src": "images/dependencies2.png",
        "alt": null
